														need.&nbsp; Let our 
														retail experience give 
														you a headstart with 
														your business.</p>
														<h3 class="auto-style2">How it works</h3>
														<ul>
															<li class="auto-style2">Meet with&nbsp;our 
															retail 
															consultants&nbsp;for 
															2 
															hours at your 
															convenience, in 
