												<article><span class="date">March 20, 2018</span>
 &nbsp;
<iframe width="360" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iRvaWHk3A8k" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>													<hr>
